msgid ""
"Easy!Appointments is a highly customizable web application that allows "
"customers to book appointments with you via a sophisticated web interface. "
"Moreover, it provides the ability to sync your data with Google Calendar so "
"you can use them with other services. It is an open source project that you "
"can download and install even for commercial use. Easy!Appointments will run "
"smoothly with your existing website as it can be installed in a single "
"folder of the server and of course share an existing database."
